{"tid":2166164,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸人成為「新加坡首富」","createTime":"2020-08-20T09:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T15:23:21.000Z","uid":134071,"like":30,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2c8354933c72bab364331f563b69da09827332ce","tid":2166164,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/111172282886558/photos/a.111246272879159/589116088425506/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F111172282886558%2Fphotos%2Fa.111246272879159%2F589116088425506%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5UBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=ff214ada\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/111172282886558/photos/a.111246272879159/589116088425506/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n獅子島上: 新加坡人生活日記<br />\n5 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n新加坡人多麽地喜歡吃海底撈，喜歡到讓前中華人民共和國公民的張勇，成爲本年度新加坡首富。<br />\n<br />\n「財經雜誌《福布斯亞洲》（Forbes Asia）今早發布最新的新加坡50大富豪榜。如今已是新加坡公民的張勇夫婦，繼續蟬聯榜首，以190億美元（約260億新元）的身家登上新加坡首富之位。張勇是火鍋連鎖店海底撈集團創始人及主席。 <br />\n<br />\n排名第二的是中國深圳上市公司邁瑞醫療（Mindray Bio-Medical Electronics）的聯合創始人兼董事長李西廷。他與張勇一樣，現為新加坡公民，是首次登上新加坡富豪榜，身家為178億美元。<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：新加坡《聯合早報》<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源： 中華人民共和國網站《搜狐》"},{"pid":"aa791df6e525fba463e0d109a28fe563a055dcb2","tid":2166164,"uid":134071,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:17:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BC%A0%E5%8B%87_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25BC%25A0%25E5%258B%2587_&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5UBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=79a95e53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%BC%A0%E5%8B%87_</a>(%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%B6)<br />\n<br />\n張勇（1974年－），四川簡陽人，現任海底撈董事長，國籍新加坡[1]。2019年至2020年登上福布斯《新加坡50大富豪榜》榜首，成為新加坡首富[2]。"},{"pid":"205697866dd144a1d6d28011570a93740db4c85f","tid":2166164,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:17:33.000Z","msg":"真係入哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e806da025b2d0122075217a3bf447a8b57cd94","tid":2166164,"uid":243677,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"想知小紅粉點睇 中國有錢有權既都有外國戶籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b21cc851a4997c5ae7d12584a4376c7601625f","tid":2166164,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d7e806da025b2d0122075217a3bf447a8b57cd94","tid":2166164,"uid":243677,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"想知小紅粉點睇 中國有錢有權既都有外國戶籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:23:00.000Z","msg":"要出動戰狼追數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df29f79cc8cb04814b7e7fb49efa401c3364ff5b","tid":2166164,"uid":189109,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C9MTEsQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC9MTEsQ.jpg&h=a6105921&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"419106b7cdb58333fa950ef19214e1b07a8e35bb","tid":2166164,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"df29f79cc8cb04814b7e7fb49efa401c3364ff5b","tid":2166164,"uid":189109,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C9MTEsQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC9MTEsQ.jpg&h=a6105921&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a2425b1e734e9b93